# Privacy Policy for CompressX

Last Updated: June 2026

CompressX ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our application collects, uses, and protects your information.

## Information We Collect

CompressX is designed to compress and optimize files directly on your device.

We may collect:

* Device information (Android version, device model)
* App usage and performance data
* Crash reports and diagnostics
* Advertising identifiers (if ads are enabled)

## Files and Media Access

CompressX may request permission to access:

* Images
* Videos
* Documents
* Other files selected by you

These permissions are used only to provide file compression and optimization features. Your files are processed locally on your device unless you explicitly choose a cloud-based feature.

## Data Sharing

We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information.

We may share limited technical information with trusted third-party services such as:

* Google Play Services
* Firebase Analytics
* Firebase Crashlytics
* AdMob (if advertisements are displayed)

These services may collect information according to their own privacy policies.

## Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect user information. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

## Children's Privacy

CompressX is not directed toward children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

## Third-Party Services

Our application may use third-party services including:

* Google Play Services
* Firebase
* Google AdMob

Please review their respective privacy policies for additional information.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.

